n itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb"><a itemprop="url" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/category/apjaktu/"><span itemprop="title">APJAKTU</span></a></span><span class="fusion-breadcrumb-sep">/</span><span class="breadcrumb-leaf">M.Tech Supplementary Exam registration is open</span></div>\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<main id="main" role="main" class="clearfix " style="">\n\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-row" style="">\n<section id="content" style="width: 100%;">\n\t\t\t\t<div class="single-navigation clearfix">\n\t\t\t<div class="fusion-single-navigation-wrapper">\n\t\t\t\t<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/mca-project-submission-last-date-extended/" rel="prev">Previous</a>\t\t\t\t<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/b-tech-s7-s-exam-may-2019-supplementary-regn-is-opened/" rel="next">Next</a>\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<article id="post-19083" class="post post-19083 type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-apjaktu">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title fusion-post-title">M.Tech Supplementary Exam registration is open</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="post-content">\n\t\t\t\t<p>The Supplementary exam registration for the following M.Tech exams are open from 14-6-19 to 16-6-19 for students and college submission is on 17-6-19.M.Tech S1 (S) Exam July 2019 (FT), M.Tech S1 (S) Exam July 2019 (PT), M.Tech S3 (S) Exam June 2019 (FT), M.Tech S3 (S) Exam June 2019 (PT), M.Tech S4 (R&amp;S) Exam June 2019 (PT), M.Tech S4 (R&amp;S) Exam June 2019 (FT) , M.Tech S5 (S) Exam June 2019 (PT).</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-meta-info"><div class="fusion-meta-info-wrapper">By <span class="vcard"><span class="fn"><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/author/webadmin/" title="Posts by Software Development Center" rel="author">Software Development Center</a></span></spa