"fusion-text"><p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://ktu.edu.in/Menu/announcements">View All &gt;&gt;</a></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:100px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1  fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last fusion-blend-mode 1_1"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="background-color:#87aff4;padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-one" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;"><h1 class="title-heading-center"><span style="color: #ffffff;">COLLABORATIONS &amp; MoU’s</span></h1></div><div class="fusion-section-separator section-separator" style="border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;margin-left:-0px;margin-right:-0px;"><div class="divider-candy-arrow bottom" style="top:0px;border-top-color: #87aff4;"></div><div class="divider-candy bottom" style="bottom:-21px;border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;border-left:1px solid #87aff4;"></div></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-first 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-7 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IIT-Bombay-800x667-compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" title="IIT-Bombay-800&#215;667-compressed" class="img-responsive wp-image-15402" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IIT-Bombay-800x667-compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IIT-Bombay-800x667-compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IIT-Bombay-800x667-compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IIT-Bombay-800x667-compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">Collaboration with IIT Bombay</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>The Spoken Tutorial project is the initiative of the ‘Talk to a Teacher’ activity of the National Mission on Education through Information and Communication Technology (ICT), launched by the Ministry of Human Resources and Development, Government of India. The Spoken Tutorial project is being developed by IIT Bombay for MHRD, Government of India.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-8 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/6-800x667-compressd-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" title="6-800&#215;667-compressd" class="img-responsive wp-image-15400" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/6-800x667-compressd-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/6-800x667-compressd-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/6-800x667-compressd-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/6-800x667-compressd.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">COLLABORATION WITH IIT MADRAS</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p style="text-align: left;">NPTEL is the largest repository of online courses in Engineering, Science &amp; Humanities from India’s best Institutes. Students can experience class room like learning from the experts. SJCET Palai is now a Local Chapter of NPTEL managed by IIT Madras. The students of SJCET can access all the courses of NPTEL even without an Internet connection.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-text"><p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/nptel/">More &gt;&gt;</a></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-last 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-9 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/KSUM-SJCET-800x667-compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" title="KSUM-SJCET-800&#215;667-compressed" class="img-responsive wp-image-15398" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/KSUM-SJCET-800x667-compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/KSUM-SJCET-800x667-compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/KSUM-SJCET-800x667-compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/KSUM-SJCET-800x667-compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">IEDC @ SJCET Palai</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p style="text-align: left;">St. Joseph&#8217;s College of Engineering &amp; Technology, Palai has collaborated with the Kerala Startup Mission, for promoting Innovation &amp; Entrepreneurship ecosystem  with in the campus</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-first 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-10 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ASAP-SJCET-800x667-compressed-400x334-1-300x251.jpg" width="300" height="251" alt="" title="ASAP-SJCET-800&#215;667-compressed-400&#215;334" class="img-responsive wp-image-19843" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ASAP-SJCET-800x667-compressed-400x334-1-200x167.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ASAP-SJCET-800x667-compressed-400x334-1.jpg 400w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">MoU with ASAP</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>Additional Skill Acquisition Programme (ASAP) , a joint initiative of General and Higher Education Departments, was launched with an objective to impart quality skill education to the higher secondary / undergraduate students alongwith their regular curriculum.SJCET Palai signed MoU with ASAP to deliver skill based courses for the students.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-11 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/ICTAK-SJCET-800x667-compressed-400x334-300x251.jpg" width="" height="" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive"/></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">MoU WITH ICT Academy of Kerala</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p style="text-align: left;">SJCET is now a Premium Member of ICT Academy of Kerala. As part of this membership ICTAK  will help the students, the teachers and the institution in the skill development through various programmes.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-last 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span style="-webkit-border-radius:50%;-moz-border-radius:50%;border-radius:50%;-webkit-mask-image: -webkit-radial-gradient(circle, white, black);" class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-12 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/GitHub-Campus-SJCET-Palai-300x251.jpg" width="300" height="251" alt="" title="GitHub-Campus-SJCET-Palai" class="img-responsive wp-image-21762" style="-webkit-border-radius:50%;-moz-border-radius:50%;border-radius:50%;" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/GitHub-Campus-SJCET-Palai-200x167.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/GitHub-Campus-SJCET-Palai.jpg 400w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">SJCET Palai is a GitHub Campus</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>Get ready to explore the world’s leading software development platform! Being one of the ten official GitHub Campus program partner Colleges in Kerala, SJCET has strengthened its high-tech programming curriculum. Our partnership with GitHub now enables the students to get free access to the GitHub Student Developer Pack. This streamlines the move from theoretical into practical skills, as well as gives real-world tools needed in the tech trade.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-first 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-13 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/redhat-academy-sjcet-300x251.jpg" width="300" height="251" alt="" title="redhat-academy-sjcet" class="img-responsive wp-image-20124" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/redhat-academy-sjcet-200x167.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/redhat-academy-sjcet.jpg 400w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">MoU with Redhat</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>SJCET PALAI have entered a MoU with Red Hat® – the World’s largest Linux Company, to become a RedHat Academy. Through this academic partnership, Red Hat® is providing training and certification programmes in today’s most demanded globally recognized IT certifications at our campus.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-text"><p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/sjcet-redhat-academy/">More &gt;&gt;</a></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-14 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/UIPath-SJCET-300x251.jpg" width="300" height="251" alt="" title="UIPath SJCET" class="img-responsive wp-image-20131" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/UIPath-SJCET-200x167.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/UIPath-SJCET.jpg 400w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">MoU with UiPath</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p><span id="hs_cos_wrapper_module_153900657322074_" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text">SJCET Signed MoU with UiPath, a <span class="st">leading Robotic Process Automation vendor</span>. This MoU empowers students with automation skills on campus through specially designed <strong>Robotic Process Automation (RPA)</strong> curricula, the <strong>UiPath software platform</strong>, supporting forums, and collaboration tools.</span></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-text"><p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/uipath-academic-alliance-sjcet-palai/">More &gt;&gt;</a></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-last 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-15 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Oracle-Academy-new-300x251.jpg" width="300" height="251" alt="" title="Oracle-Academy-new" class="img-responsive wp-image-20129" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Oracle-Academy-new-200x167.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Oracle-Academy-new.jpg 400w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">MoU with Oracle</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>Oracle Academy provides educational institutions with the resources they need to help educators develop core computing knowledge and skills aligned to industry standards and using current technologies that they can teach students, the skills they need to succeed. The program offers institutions and educators access to a wide range of teaching and educational resources, including curriculum, classroom learning resources, software, cloud technology, practice environments, and much more. SJCET Palai signed MoU with Oracle to bring this cutting edge to students.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-text"><p style="text-align: right;"><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/oracle-academy-sjcet-palai/">More &gt;&gt;</a></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:100px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:100px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1  fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last fusion-blend-mode 1_1"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="background-color:#87aff4;padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-one" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;"><h1 class="title-heading-center"><span style="color: #ffffff;">CAMPUS ACTIVITIES</span></h1></div><div class="fusion-section-separator section-separator" style="border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;margin-left:-0px;margin-right:-0px;"><div class="divider-candy-arrow bottom" style="top:0px;border-top-color: #87aff4;"></div><div class="divider-candy bottom" style="bottom:-21px;border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;border-left:1px solid #87aff4;"></div></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_4  fusion-one-fourth fusion-column-first 1_4"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:25%;width:calc(25% - ( ( 4% + 4% + 4% ) * 0.25 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-16 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Sargam-SJCET-Palai-800x667-300x250.png" width="" height="" alt="" title="" class="img-responsive"/></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">SARGAM- ANNUAL CULTURAL FESTIVAL</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>SJCET Palai is actively engaged in providing the students with an extensive range of cultural and co-curricular activities. Keeping in line with this commitment our college organizes Annual Cultural Fest Sargam. It embodies eagerly awaited multiple events in dance, music, fashion, drama, literary and various other cultural fields and offers a plethora of opportunities to the students to showcase their talent.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_4  fusion-one-fourth 1_4"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:25%;width:calc(25% - ( ( 4% + 4% + 4% ) * 0.25 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-17 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Asthra-SJCET-Palai-800x667-compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" title="Asthra-SJCET-Palai-800&#215;667-compressed" class="img-responsive wp-image-15412" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Asthra-SJCET-Palai-800x667-compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Asthra-SJCET-Palai-800x667-compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Asthra-SJCET-Palai-800x667-compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Asthra-SJCET-Palai-800x667-compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 600px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">ASTHRA -ANNUAL TECHNICAL FEST</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>Asthra is the annual technical festival of SJCET Palai. With an annual footfall of more than 5,000 visitors and participants, Asthra is one of the biggest inter-college fests in Kerala. Asthra will keep you engrossed in a plethora of professional shows, competitions, lectures and workshops that have a lot to offer to everybody.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_4  fusion-one-fourth 1_4"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:25%;width:calc(25% - ( ( 4% + 4% + 4% ) * 0.25 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-18 hover-type-zoomin"><a class="fusion-no-lightbox" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/ncc-sjcet/" target="_self" aria-label="NCC PNG"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/NCC-PNG-300x251.png" width="300" height="251" alt="" class="img-responsive wp-image-21099" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/NCC-PNG-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/NCC-PNG.png 400w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">NCC</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>SJCET has the rare honor of being the first self-financing engineering college to have an NCC unit (Army wing with an authorized strength of 160 cadets) NCC aims at developing character, comradeship, discipline, secular outlook, spirit of adventure and ideals of selfless service among young citizens. Further, it aims to create a pool of well organized and trained youth with leadership qualities, motivated to serve the nation and contribute to the national development. The motto of NCC is Unity and Discipline. <a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/ncc-sjcet/">Read More&#8230;</a></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_4  fusion-one-fourth fusion-column-last 1_4"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:25%;width:calc(25% - ( ( 4% + 4% + 4% ) * 0.25 ) );'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-19 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/NSS-800x667compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" title="NSS-800x667compressed" class="img-responsive wp-image-15418" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/NSS-800x667compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/NSS-800x667compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/NSS-800x667compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/NSS-800x667compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 600px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">NSS</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>SJCET NSS unit is affiliated to department of Technical Education , Government of Kerala .It was inaugurated on 27-04-2008 by Mr K. A .Kalith programme coordinator, RIT, pampady. The motto or watchword of the National Service Scheme is &#8216;NOT ME BUT YOU&#8217;. This reflects the essence of democratic living and upholds the need for selfless service and appreciation of the other person&#8217;s point of view and also shows consideration for fellow human beings. It underlines that the welfare of an individual is ultimately dependent on the welfare of society as a whole. Therefore, it should be the aim of the NSS to demonstrate this motto in its day-to-day programme</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:100px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:100px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1  fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last fusion-blend-mode 1_1"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="background-color:#87aff4;padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-one" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;"><h1 class="title-heading-center"><span style="color: #ffffff;">ENTREPRENEURIAL INITIATIVES</span></h1></div><div class="fusion-section-separator section-separator" style="border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;margin-left:-0px;margin-right:-0px;"><div class="divider-candy-arrow bottom" style="top:0px;border-top-color: #87aff4;"></div><div class="divider-candy bottom" style="bottom:-21px;border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;border-left:1px solid #87aff4;"></div></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_4  fusion-one-fourth fusion-column-first 1_4"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:25%;width:calc(25% - ( ( 4% + 4% + 4% ) * 0.25 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-20 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bootcamp-icon-800x667compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" title="bootcamp-icon-800x667compressed" class="img-responsive wp-image-15420" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bootcamp-icon-800x667compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bootcamp-icon-800x667compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bootcamp-icon-800x667compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/bootcamp-icon-800x667compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 600px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">SJCET BOOTCAMP</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p style="text-align: left;">As part of promoting the entrepreneurship culture among students, the St. Joseph’s College of Engineering and Technology, Palai (SJCET PALAI), in association with the Kerala Startup Mission, has decided to set up an Innovation &amp; Entrepreneurship Development Center(SJCET Startup BootCamp) at the college. It was inaugurated on the 9th of march, 2015.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_4  fusion-one-fourth 1_4"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:25%;width:calc(25% - ( ( 4% + 4% + 4% ) * 0.25 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-21 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/EDC-icon-800x667compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" title="EDC-icon-800x667compressed" class="img-responsive wp-image-15421" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/EDC-icon-800x667compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/EDC-icon-800x667compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/EDC-icon-800x667compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/EDC-icon-800x667compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 600px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">ENTREPRENEURSHIP DEVELOPMENT CLUB</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>Department of Industries &amp; Commerce, Government of Kerala formulated a scheme to set up Entrepreneurship Development Clubs in schools and colleges of the State to inculcate Entrepreneurial Culture amongst youth and equip them with the skills, techniques and confidence to act as torch-bearers of Enterprise for the new generation.SJCET Palai started ED club in the year 2006.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_4  fusion-one-fourth 1_4"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:25%;width:calc(25% - ( ( 4% + 4% + 4% ) * 0.25 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-22 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/maker-space-icon-800x667compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" title="maker-space-icon-800x667compressed" class="img-responsive wp-image-15422" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/maker-space-icon-800x667compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/maker-space-icon-800x667compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/maker-space-icon-800x667compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/maker-space-icon-800x667compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 600px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">MAKER SPACE</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>A makerspace is a collaborative work space inside SJCET Palai for making, learning, exploring and sharing that uses high tech to no tech tools. This space are open to students and have a variety of maker equipment including 3D printers, developer boards, soldering irons etc. This is a joint initiative by Kerala Startup Mission and SJCET Palai.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_4  fusion-one-fourth fusion-column-last 1_4"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:25%;width:calc(25% - ( ( 4% + 4% + 4% ) * 0.25 ) );'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-23 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iic-SJCET.jpg" width="300" height="251" alt="" title="iic SJCET" class="img-responsive wp-image-20097" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iic-SJCET-200x167.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/iic-SJCET.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">IIC SJCET</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>Ministry of Human Resource Development, Govt. of India has established an ‘Innovation cell’ with a purpose of systematically fostering the culture of Innovation in all Higher Education Institutions (HEIs) across the country.As part of this initiative an Institutions Innovation Council is established in SJCET Palai</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:100px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:100px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1  fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last fusion-blend-mode 1_1"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="background-color:#87aff4;padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-one" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;"><h1 class="title-heading-center"><span style="color: #ffffff;">PROFESSIONAL SOCIETIES</span></h1></div><div class="fusion-section-separator section-separator" style="border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;margin-left:-0px;margin-right:-0px;"><div class="divider-candy-arrow bottom" style="top:0px;border-top-color: #87aff4;"></div><div class="divider-candy bottom" style="bottom:-21px;border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;border-left:1px solid #87aff4;"></div></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-first 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-24 hover-type-zoomin"><a class="fusion-no-lightbox" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/ieee-sjcet/" target="_self" aria-label="IEEE-LOGO-800&#215;667-compressed"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IEEE-LOGO-800x667-compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" class="img-responsive wp-image-15425" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IEEE-LOGO-800x667-compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IEEE-LOGO-800x667-compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IEEE-LOGO-800x667-compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/IEEE-LOGO-800x667-compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center"><span style="color: #000000;">THE INSTITUTE OF ELECTRICAL AND ELECTRONICS ENGINEERS @ SJCET Palai</span></h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p><strong>IEEE</strong> opens the door to opportunities that will help students to develop their professional identity in IEEE&#8217;s designated fields of interest: sciences, technology, engineering, and mathematics (STEM). In addition to accessing a range of membership benefits, students will make global connections with people who can help students along their targeted career path through IEEE&#8217;s international community of members and volunteers. <a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/ieee-sjcet/">Read More&#8230;</a></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-25 hover-type-zoomin"><a class="fusion-no-lightbox" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/csi/" target="_self" aria-label="17-800x667compressed"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-800x667compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" class="img-responsive wp-image-15426" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-800x667compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-800x667compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-800x667compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/17-800x667compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">COMPUTER SOCIETY OF INDIA</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>Computer Society of India is the first and largest body of computer professionals in India. It was started on 6 March 1965 by a few computer professionals and has now grown to be the national body representing computer professionals. It has 72 chapters across India, 511 student branches, and 100,000 members. <a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/csi/">Read More&#8230;</a></p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-last 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-26 hover-type-zoomin"><a class="fusion-no-lightbox" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/sae/" target="_self" aria-label="sae-600&#215;500"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/sae-600x500-1-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" class="img-responsive wp-image-27569" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/sae-600x500-1-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/sae-600x500-1-400x333.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/sae-600x500-1.png 600w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">SOCIETY OF AUTOMOTIVE ENGINEERS INDIA @ SJCET Palai</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>SAEINDIA is India&#8217;s leading resource for mobility technology. As an individual member driven society of mobility practitioners the ownership of SAEINDIA wrests with its members who are Individuals from the mobility community, which includes Engineers Executives from Industry, Government Officials, Academics and Students</p>\n<p>SAEINDIA is an affiliate society of SAE International registered in India as an Indian nonprofit engineering and scientific society dedicated to the advancement of mobility industry in India.</p>\n<p>SAEINDIA Collegiate clubs offer well organized programs and activities, fellowship, and leadership experience to student members. SAEINDIA student members are also entitled to many of the services available to SAEINDIA members.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-first 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-27 hover-type-zoomin"><a class="fusion-no-lightbox" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/iste/" target="_self" aria-label="ISTE-SJCET-Palai-800x667compressed"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ISTE-SJCET-Palai-800x667compressed-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" class="img-responsive wp-image-15431" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ISTE-SJCET-Palai-800x667compressed-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ISTE-SJCET-Palai-800x667compressed-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ISTE-SJCET-Palai-800x667compressed-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/ISTE-SJCET-Palai-800x667compressed.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">THE INDIAN SOCIETY FOR TECHNICAL EDUCATION @ SJCET Palai</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>Indian Society for Technical Education (ISTE) is the leading National Professional non-profit making Society for the Technical Education in the field of engineering and technology registered under the Societies Registration Act of 1860. The organization established in the year 1941 with the motto of Career Development of Engineering Teachers and Personality Development of Students and overall development of our Technical Education System. ISTE serves as a platform for educators, researchers and professionals to exchange ideas, enhance skills, and contribute to the advancement of engineering and technology education.<br />\nThe major objective of the ISTE, SJCET Chapter is to provide quality training programmes to update knowledge and skills of teachers and students in their field. SJCET chapter regularly conducts training programmes for newly inducted teachers, short term training programmes on outcome-based education, guidance and counselling and so on.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-last 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-28 hover-type-zoomin"><a class="fusion-no-lightbox" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/asme/" target="_self" aria-label="asme-NEWLOGO"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/asme-NEWLOGO-300x250.png" width="300" height="250" alt="" class="img-responsive wp-image-29865" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/asme-NEWLOGO-200x167.png 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/asme-NEWLOGO-400x334.png 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/asme-NEWLOGO-600x500.png 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/asme-NEWLOGO.png 800w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 300px" /></a></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">ASME STUDENT CHAPTER</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>The ASME SJCET student chapter at the college was formed on 25th January, 2018 with the motto “Excellence is our obsession” and “Synergy at work”. The chapter focuses on providing training to the students to become experts in learning; on encouraging innovation and excellence in students through various means; on promoting better career development opportunities and services for students; on arranging expert industrial and research lectures; on extending full support for all the national seminars and technical events in the college; and on enhancing the self-confidence and self-esteem of students.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:100px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_1  fusion-one-full fusion-column-first fusion-column-last fusion-blend-mode 1_1"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="background-color:#87aff4;padding: 10px 0px 10px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-one" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;"><h1 class="title-heading-center"><span style="color: #ffffff;">ACHIEVEMENTS &amp; AWARDS</span></h1></div><div class="fusion-section-separator section-separator" style="border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;margin-left:-0px;margin-right:-0px;"><div class="divider-candy-arrow bottom" style="top:0px;border-top-color: #87aff4;"></div><div class="divider-candy bottom" style="bottom:-21px;border-bottom:1px solid #87aff4;border-left:1px solid #87aff4;"></div></div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div><div class="fusion-fullwidth fullwidth-box nonhundred-percent-fullwidth non-hundred-percent-height-scrolling"  style='background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0);background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;padding-top:0px;padding-right:0px;padding-bottom:0px;padding-left:0px;'><div class="fusion-builder-row fusion-row "><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-first 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-29 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/arawd2025.jpg" width="1200" height="752" alt="" title="arawd2025" class="img-responsive wp-image-30890" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/arawd2025-200x125.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/arawd2025-400x251.jpg 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/arawd2025-600x376.jpg 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/arawd2025-800x501.jpg 800w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/arawd2025.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 1200px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">2 Million Karma point milestone award</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>St. Joseph’s College of Engineering and Technology, Palai (Autonomous), has been honored with the &#8220;<strong>2 Million Karma Award</strong>&#8221; under the Milestone Award category by <strong>GTech µLearn at Permute 2025</strong>. The µLearn platform fosters a culture of collaboration, breaks through echo chambers, and empowers learners to upskill and evolve.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );margin-right: 4%;'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-30 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/award2.jpg" width="1200" height="752" alt="" title="award2" class="img-responsive wp-image-30892" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/award2-200x125.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/award2-400x251.jpg 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/award2-600x376.jpg 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/award2-800x501.jpg 800w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/award2.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 1200px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">Net Zero Carbon Kerala</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>St. Joseph’s College of Engineering and Technology, Palai (Autonomous) has been honored with a prestigious certificate from the Government of Kerala for its exemplary efforts in achieving net zero emissions. SJCET Palai remains committed to environmental responsibility, actively contributing to the fight against climate change.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div><div  class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion_builder_column_1_3  fusion-one-third fusion-column-last 1_3"  style='margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:20px;width:33.33%;width:calc(33.33% - ( ( 4% + 4% ) * 0.3333 ) );'>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column-wrapper" style="padding: 0px 0px 0px 0px;background-position:left top;background-repeat:no-repeat;-webkit-background-size:cover;-moz-background-size:cover;-o-background-size:cover;background-size:cover;"  data-bg-url="">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="imageframe-align-center"><span class="fusion-imageframe imageframe-none imageframe-31 hover-type-zoomin"><img loading="lazy" src="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NASSCOM-MOU.jpg" width="1200" height="752" alt="" title="NASSCOM-MOU" class="img-responsive wp-image-30895" srcset="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NASSCOM-MOU-200x125.jpg 200w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NASSCOM-MOU-400x251.jpg 400w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NASSCOM-MOU-600x376.jpg 600w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NASSCOM-MOU-800x501.jpg 800w, https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/NASSCOM-MOU.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 1200px" /></span></div><div class="fusion-title title fusion-sep-none fusion-title-center fusion-title-size-two" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;"><h2 class="title-heading-center">MoU with NASSCOM</h2></div><div class="fusion-text"><p>St. Joseph’s College of Engineering and Technology, Palai (Autonomous), has signed an MoU with NASSCOM/IT-ITeS Sector Skills Council to boost skill development in emerging technologies. Through this collaboration, students and faculty will access industry-aligned courses, certifications, and assessments via the Future Skills Prime platform to enhance their career prospects.</p>\n</div><div class="fusion-clearfix"></div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t</div>  <!-- fusion-row -->\n\t\t\t</main>  <!-- #main -->\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-footer">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t<footer role="contentinfo" class="fusion-footer-widget-area fusion-widget-area">\n\t\t<div class="fusion-row">\n\t\t\t<div class="fusion-columns fusion-columns-4 fusion-widget-area">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-column col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section id="text-6" class="fusion-footer-widget-column widget widget_text"><h4 class="widget-title">Important Links</h4>\t\t\t<div class="textwidget"><p><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/">Home</a><br />\n<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/telephone-directory/">Telephone Directory</a><br />\n<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/student-verification/">Student Verification &#8211; </a>9495684408<br />\n<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/SJCET_EOA-2002-TO-2021-22.pdf">EOA Report 2002-2021</a><br />\n<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/EOA_Report_2019-20.pdf">EOA Report 2019-2020</a><br />\n<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/CorrigendumEOA_Report_2020-21.pdf">EOA Report 2020-2021</a><br />\n<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/ACFrOgBLY79QsTIqHDtgMz-uWXxM2qY0PYS_NQz2vsdFaxRe1h4_QbBhBMrInVGm99R-035Gb6zzbQH4nocGxxTrEXIlrOYgAKeHBsyB1gfJnx3U2gqtoLEgtf7K6nE.pdf">EOA Report 2021-2022</a><br />\n<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/EOA_Report_22-23.pdf">EOA Report 2022-2023</a><br />\n<a h