="fusion-page-title-captions">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class="entry-title">Postponement of B.Tech S.7 (Suppl.) Examinations scheduled on 14th &#038; 18th June, 2019 &#8211; Reg</h1>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-page-title-secondary">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-breadcrumbs"><span itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb"><a itemprop="url" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in"><span itemprop="title">Home</span></a></span><span class="fusion-breadcrumb-sep">/</span><span itemscope itemtype="http://data-vocabulary.org/Breadcrumb"><a itemprop="url" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/category/apjaktu/"><span itemprop="title">APJAKTU</span></a></span><span class="fusion-breadcrumb-sep">/</span><span class="breadcrumb-leaf">Postponement of B.Tech S.7 (Suppl.) Examinations scheduled on 14th &#038; 18th June, 2019 &#8211; Reg</span></div>\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<main id="main" role="main" class="clearfix " style="">\n\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-row" style="">\n<section id="content" style="width: 100%;">\n\t\t\t\t<div class="single-navigation clearfix">\n\t\t\t<div class="fusion-single-navigation-wrapper">\n\t\t\t\t<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/m-tech-s2/" rel="prev">Previous</a>\t\t\t\t<a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/mca-second-year-direct-s4-s-exam-dec-2018-results-published/" rel="next">Next</a>\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<article id="post-19046" class="post post-19046 type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-apjaktu">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class="entry-title fusion-post-title">Postponement of B.Tech S.7 (Suppl.) Examinations scheduled on 14th &#038; 18th June, 2019 &#8211; Reg</h2>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="post-content">\n\t\t\t\t<p>The revaluation results of B.Tech S.7, December 2018 is yet to be published and only on publishing the same, the supplementary examination registration can be opened. Hence it is notified for the information of all concerned that <a href="http://www.artdesignandpublicity.com/" title="artdesignandpublicity" style="text-decoration:none;color:#333;">artdesignandpublicity</a> B.Tech S.7 (Suppl.) Examinations scheduled on 14th &amp; 18th June, 2019 have been postponed, the revised dates being 22nd June, AN &amp; 3rd July, AN, 2019 respectively.</p>\n<p><span style="color: #0000ff;"><a style="color: #0000ff;" href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/PostponementofB.TechS_.7Suppl.Examinations.pdf">Notification</a></span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-meta-info"><div class="fusion-meta-info-wrapper">By <span class="vcard"><span class="fn"><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/author/webadmin/" title="Posts by Software Development Center" rel="author">Software Development Center</a></span></span><span class="fusion-inline-sep">|</span>\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t<span class="updated rich-snippet-hidden">\n\t\t\t2025-07-29T06:23:17+00:00\t\t</span>\n\t\n<span>June 11th, 2019</span><span class="fusion-inline-sep">|</span><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/category/apjaktu/" rel="category tag">APJAKTU</a><span class="fusion-inline-sep">|</span><span class="fusion-comments"><a href="https://sjcetpalai.ac.in/postponement-of-b-tech-s-7-suppl-examinations-scheduled-on-14th-18th-june-2019-reg/#respond">0 Comments</a></span></div></div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class="related-posts single-related-posts">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="fusion-title fusion-title-size-three sep-double" style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:31px;">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class="title-heading-left">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRelated Posts\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class="title-sep-container">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class="title-sep sep-double"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class="